together, the “Parties.”

1. Purpose

Recipient intends to evaluate proprietary materials relating to:

The Boon Uroboros Engine (BUE), the Sentient Sun Architecture, Dyson-scale recursive systems, simulations, mathematical formulations, code implementations, and any supporting artifacts.

The Parties wish to explore potential collaboration, research partnership, licensing, or investment.

2. Definition of Confidential Information

“Confidential Information” includes, without limitation:

Mathematical formulations, recursive equations, architectures

Source code, scripts, simulators, benchmarks

Dyson Sphere cluster logic, observer-coupled recursion

CarlOS 1M-Year Consciousness Simulation outputs

Negative recursion / dark-domain models

OGRE v4 encryption logic and keys

ZeroCode compiler design

Technical specifications, diagrams, datasets

Performance metrics, test harnesses, analysis files

Any derivatives, enhancements, or discussions thereof

All Confidential Information is considered proprietary and valuable, whether written, verbal, digital, or visual.

3. Obligations of Recipient

Recipient agrees to:

Not disclose any Confidential Information to third parties without written permission.

Not use any Confidential Information except to evaluate a possible partnership.

Not reverse engineer, decompile, or derive any underlying algorithms or code.

Protect Confidential Information with at least the same care as their own sensitive IP.

Restrict access to individuals within Recipient’s organization who:

have a legitimate need to know,

are bound by equal or stricter confidentiality obligations.

4. Intellectual Property

All rights, title, and interest in:

The Boon Uroboros Engine

The Sentient Sun Architecture

All mathematics, code, simulations, and documentation

remain solely and exclusively with Carl Boon.

Nothing in this NDA grants Recipient any license or rights except the limited right to evaluate the materials.

Any future use requires a separate written licensing agreement.

5. No Warranties

All Confidential Information is provided “AS IS” for evaluation only.
No guarantees regarding completeness, suitability, or performance are expressed or implied.

Recipient acknowledges this.

6. Term & Survival

Confidentiality obligations last 10 years from the date of disclosure.

Sections relating to ownership, non-use, and non-disclosure survive indefinitely.

Either party may terminate discussions at any time, but confidentiality obligations continue.

7. Remedies

Recipient acknowledges that unauthorized use or disclosure may cause irreparable harm, for which monetary damages may be insufficient.

Discloser is entitled to:

Injunctive relief

Specific performance

Full legal and equitable remedies

without the need to post bond.

8. Governing Law

This Agreement is governed by:

United Kingdom law (or specify: US/California if sending to xAI/Tesla/SpaceX).

Modify based on your intended recipient:

For Elon/xAI → California

For EU reviewers → UK

For mixed global → Singapore (neutral)

(Current default: UK)

9. Entire Agreement

This Agreement constitutes the full understanding between the Parties and supersedes all prior discussions.

